%% Diagram: EME / CDM license acquisition for encrypted playback
%% Type: sequence
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant V as HTMLMediaElement
    participant JS as Player (JS)
    participant CDM as CDM (Widevine / FairPlay / PlayReady)
    participant LS as License Server
    participant Origin as Origin / CDN

    Origin-->>V: init segment with PSSH box
    V->>JS: encrypted event (initData, initDataType)
    JS->>JS: navigator.requestMediaKeySystemAccess()
    JS->>CDM: createMediaKeys / createSession
    CDM-->>JS: message event (license challenge)
    JS->>LS: POST license challenge (auth, device cert)
    LS-->>JS: signed license response (content key)
    JS->>CDM: session.update(license)
    CDM->>V: decrypt sample data (in TEE for L1 / SL3000)
    V-->>JS: timeupdate, playback continues
    Note over JS,LS: Renew before expiry (e.g. at ~80%)<br/>to avoid mid-stream stall
